# RDF Changelog

## 2.1.0 (2026-03-16)

### GitHub Issue Model v2 — Phase-Level Tracking + Roadmap Planning
[New] type:initiative and type:release labels in label taxonomy
[New] Target Date field (DATE) in ecosystem project setup
[New] Initiative issue type for roadmap planning (directional time-boxed)
[New] Release issue type for versioned release tracking
[New] Two-horizon roadmap: Planning Roadmap (Target Date) + Execution Roadmap (Release)
[New] Diagram 9: Issue Hierarchy (initiative → release → phase → comments)
[New] Diagram 10: Two-Horizon Roadmap visualization
[Change] Issue tracking granularity from per-task to per-phase (~72% API call reduction)
[Change] Task progress tracked via phase issue comments, not separate issues
[Change] mgr command: phase-level issue management, initiative awareness
[Change] sys-eng command: task-completion comments, phase issue commit refs
[Change] sys-qa command: QA verdict comments on phase issues
[Change] sys-sentinel agent: findings posted as phase issue comments
[Change] refresh command: removed task issue sync, added initiative/release sync
[Change] rel-prep/rel-ship/rel-merge: type:release labels, initiative lifecycle
[Change] ecosystem-init: idempotent field updates, DATE type support
[Change] README, RDF.md, WORKFORCE.md, diagrams updated for v2 model
[Change] Core governance: issue conventions rewritten for v2

## 2.0.0 (2026-03-16)

### Phase 8 — Documentation, Archive, Cutover
[Change] Complete README.md rewrite for public release
[Change] Archive all workforce/ references to rdf/
[Change] Update parent CLAUDE.md sync rules for RDF-authoritative flow
[Change] RDF.md version target updated to release version
[New] GitHub Issues + Projects bootstrapped for RDF and ecosystem
[New] Label taxonomy synced across all rfxn repos
[New] Fresh install cutover verified — full regeneration from canonical

### Phase 7 — Project Init + Health Checker
[New] rdf init — project initialization from profile templates
[New] rdf init --batch — batch initialization for multiple projects
[New] rdf init --github — GitHub scaffolding during init
[New] rdf init --dry-run — preview mode
[New] rdf doctor — 6-category project health checker
[New] rdf doctor --all — cross-project workspace scan
[New] rdf doctor --scope — per-category filtering
[New] rdf doctor --json — machine-readable output
[Change] bin/rdf — init and doctor wired as active commands
[Fix] grep -c exit-code double-output in doctor plan check

### Phase 6 — Gemini CLI + Codex Adapters + AGENTS.md
[New] adapters/gemini-cli/adapter.sh — Gemini CLI generation
[New] adapters/gemini-cli/agent-meta.json — agent metadata for Gemini
[New] adapters/gemini-cli/command-meta.json — command descriptions for Gemini
[New] adapters/codex/adapter.sh — Codex generation (AGENTS.md + config)
[New] adapters/agents-md/adapter.sh — cross-tool AGENTS.md generation
[New] adapters/agents-md/sections.json — section definitions
[Change] lib/cmd/generate.sh — multi-adapter support (gemini-cli, codex, agents-md, all)

### Phase 4 — State Refresh + Context Anchoring
[New] lib/cmd/refresh.sh — rdf refresh command (memory/plan/github scopes)
[New] canonical/commands/refresh.md — agent-driven /refresh slash command
[Change] canonical/commands/mgr.md — consume rdf-state JSON at startup
[Change] canonical/commands/reload.md — context anchoring with rdf state
[Change] bin/rdf — activate refresh command

### Phase 5 — Agent Teams Architecture
[New] lib/dispatch.sh — mode-aware agent dispatch abstraction (subagent vs Agent Teams)
[New] lib/dispatch-agents.json — centralized agent registry (11 agents)
[New] lib/dispatch-tasks.json — pipeline task templates with dependency chains
[New] lib/cmd/dispatch.sh — rdf dispatch subcommand (agent/pipeline/status)
[New] adapters/claude-code/teams-meta.json — CC Agent Teams configuration
[New] docs/specs/agent-teams-research.md — Agent Teams API research
[New] docs/specs/dispatch-abstraction.md — dispatch interface specification
[New] docs/specs/task-based-coordination.md — file-based to task-based mapping
[Change] lib/rdf_common.sh — add rdf_feature_enabled() feature flag helper
[Change] bin/rdf — register dispatch subcommand
[Change] canonical/agents/mgr.md — dispatch modes awareness
[Change] canonical/commands/mgr.md — dispatch abstraction reference
[New] RDF_AGENT_TEAMS feature flag (default: false, opt-in for Agent Teams)

### Phase 2 — CC Adapter + State Helper + CLI + GitHub
[New] bin/rdf CLI dispatcher — Sigforge sf pattern with lazy-sourced subcommands
[New] lib/rdf_common.sh — shared init, version, path helpers, require guards
[New] rdf generate claude-code — canonical + metadata -> CC output with YAML frontmatter
[New] rdf sync — reverse flow strips frontmatter, detects drift, supports --dry-run
[New] rdf state — deterministic project state JSON in <1s (no LLM)
[New] rdf github — setup, sync-labels, ecosystem-init, ecosystem-add
[New] adapters/claude-code/agent-meta.json — CC frontmatter for all 12 agents
[New] adapters/claude-code/hooks/hooks.json — hook event definitions
[New] .claude-plugin/plugin.json — CC plugin manifest
[Change] /root/.claude/{commands,agents,scripts} now symlinked to adapter output
[Fix] Version detection handles rfxn patterns (V=, VER=, VERSION=, *_version=)
[Fix] grep -c fallback avoids doubled output (anti-pattern #29)
[Remove] overwatch-hook.sh reference from settings.json SubagentStop hooks

### Phase 1 — Canonical Migration + Naming Overhaul
[New] Canonical-first architecture — tool-agnostic storage
[New] {domain}-{role} naming convention for all agents/commands
[New] Self-verification gates in QA and Sentinel agents
[New] Scope confirmation protocol in EM/mgr command
[New] sec-eng agent and command
[New] mgr agent definition (for Agent Teams delegate mode)
[Change] workforce/ renamed to rdf/
[Change] RDF is authoritative — /root/.claude/ is deployment target, not source
[Change] All agent/command cross-references updated for new naming
[Remove] overwatch-hook.sh (Overwatch project dead)
[Remove] sync.sh and install.sh (replaced by rdf generate + rdf sync)

